com.thomsonreuters.upa.valueadd.examples.consumer

Class QueueMsgHandler

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.thomsonreuters.upa.valueadd.examples.consumer.QueueMsgHandler
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    TunnelStreamDefaultMsgCallback, TunnelStreamQueueMsgCallback, TunnelStreamStatusEventCallback

    public class QueueMsgHandler
extends java.lang.Object
implements TunnelStreamStatusEventCallback, TunnelStreamDefaultMsgCallback, TunnelStreamQueueMsgCallback
    This is the queue message handler for the UPA Value Add consumer application. It handles any queue message delivery. It only supports one ReactorChannel/TunnelStream.
